{"tid":691404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲新移民以為自已有錢就大哂","createTime":"2018-06-05T16:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:22:37.000Z","uid":171124,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4f124ba2dbec2f1d3ed90044285a2e493ad8f2","tid":691404,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"今日返返下工見到有個新移民<br />\n成家人，帶埋個印傭出黎食飯<br />\n一入到鋪頭就叫個印傭坐開啲<br />\n因為本餐牌係印傭張枱度<br />\n之後個新移民就叫個印傭拎個餐牌比佢<br />\n開頭個印傭聽得唔係好清楚<br />\n跟住個新移民就好惡咁行過去<br />\n用手指篤住印傭個頭<br />\n撚狗咁撚   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果一刻我真係覺得個印傭好慘，<br />\n大部份既人以為自已好少少錢，就洗人唔洗本<br />\n其實唔單止新移民，大部份香港人都有依個問題/行為<br />\n雖然我地未必阻止到，但至少唔好咁樣做"},{"pid":"4e8a3aa5862ebe34792090bdbf4433c48d0034f9","tid":691404,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7351429928ebbe25b327d42df902b08878a5892b","tid":691404,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"自以為"},{"pid":"50204c7e7bac8c1a7929639fda9ed512ae82f98e","tid":691404,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b305b437e9b657ad55daf801156c0ceefeabe909","tid":691404,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dbfbd379a119211c8887100356a37bbcffcf67f","tid":691404,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2c5d36953e2ad1d2592d8a5bfdbdd762d3c01069","tid":691404,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f4416843d86f5cdd3a940d4e48f9bd14a81d0d0b","tid":691404,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-